@node Web "Lottery Draw"

                                @{b}Lottery Draw@{ub}

As  you  might  have  guessed  from  the  SCREEN   tooltype   mentioned   in
@{"Configuration" Link Config}.  I have Riktor open on the screen of Voyager. I do this as I
found a rather useful web site which publishes the lottery numbers very soon
after  each  draw  as  well  as  providing details of how many winners there
were.

The URL of this rather useful site is...

        http://www.llednulb.demon.co.uk

@endnode
